Algorithm: Linear Search Using Array

Step 1: Start

Step 2: Read the size of the array and store it in variable range

Step 3: Create an integer array arr[] of size range

Step 4: Read the elements of the array using a for loop

Step 5: Read the number to be searched and store it in variable number

Step 6: Traverse the array using a for loop from i = 0 to range - 1

Step 7: Compare arr[i] with number

Step 8: If arr[i] == number,
        display the position of the element as i + 1

Step 9: Stop
